hopobject.body: Could you transfer $1000 from my current account to my deposit account? cajademedicos.com.ar In the three months ended June 30, Wii U software sales came in at just over one million, taking lifetime software sales for the console to 14.44 million. That means the current Wii U attach rate is at about four games for each console - an encouraging sign, and one which suggests the Wii U install base is predominantly core gamers.
